《'''荒原'''》（{{lang-en|''Into the Badlands''}}）是一部[[美國|美國]]的電視連續劇，於2015年11月15日首播<ref name="deadline-201507">{{cite web|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=How Martial Arts Series ''Into the Badlands'' Kicked Its Way Onto AMC; Debuts Nov. 15 – TCA|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/into-the-badlands-tca-daniel-wu-1201488844/|website=[[deadline.com|deadline.com]]|accessdate=August 2, 2015|date=July 31, 2015|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222180309/http://deadline.com/2015/07/into-the-badlands-tca-daniel-wu-1201488844/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，武打和武術動作由[[馮德倫|馮德倫]]、谷軒昭等人負責<ref name="nytstyle-t22badlands"/>。此電視影集，係關於一名戰士和一小男孩如何一起通過危險的封建土地旅程得以尋求啟迪的故事。<ref>{{cite web |title=First Look at Daniel Wu in AMC’s Into the Badlands |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/tv/trailers/424349-first-look-at-daniel-wu-in-amcs-into-the-badlands |website=Comingsoon.net |accessdate=July 27, 2015 |date=March 29, 2015 |language=en |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304025629/http://www.comingsoon.net/tv/trailers/424349-first-look-at-daniel-wu-in-amcs-into-the-badlands |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="etnet-2015-35797"/><ref name="hkappledaily-2015-54402100"/><ref name="chinayes-20151113">{{cite news |url= http://tw.twent.chinayes.com/Content/20151113/KKMIW9TIMULS.shtml |title= 《荒原》首播 吳彥祖馮德倫聯袂在美電視劇「武」出一片天 |date= 2015-11-13 |accessdate= 2016-01-05 |publisher= Yes娛樂 |author1= Yes娛樂新聞中心 |language= zh |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130856/http://tw.twent.chinayes.com/Content/20151113/KKMIW9TIMULS.shtml |archivedate= 2016-03-04 }} {{zh-tw}}</ref><ref name="nextmag-2015-28445758">{{cite news |url= http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breaking-news/entertainment/20151020/28445758 |title= 參演美劇《荒原》　吳彥祖扮戰士耍酷 |date= 2015-10-20 |accessdate= 2016-01-05 |publisher= 香港商壹傳媒 |work= 壹週刊 |author1= 娛樂組 |language= zh |archive-date= 2016-03-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305084413/http://www.nextmag.com.tw